tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE OrderHistory (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    quantity INT,
    customer_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE order_history (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    order_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE supply_chain (
    supply_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    supplier_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    delivery_date DATE,
    quantity_supplied INT
);

CREATE TABLE order_history (
	order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	order_date DATE,
	customer_id INT,
	product_id INT,
	quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE supply_chain (
	supply_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	supply_date DATE,
	product_id INT,
	upplier_id INT,
	supply_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  product_id INT,
  order_date DATE,
  quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE shipments (
  shipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  order_id INT,
  shipment_date DATE,
  carrier VARCHAR(50),
  tracking_number VARCHAR(20)
);
